y NYC App for IOS"\n     - Android: "Download the Ready NYC App for Android"\n   - The app stores preparedness information and can receive alerts directly on your phone.\n3. **Wireless Emergency Alerts (WEA)**\n   - These are automatic alerts sent to compatible wireless phones (e.g., Amber alerts).\n   - For more details, click the "More Information on Wireless Emergency Alerts" link.\n\nBy following any of these methods—registering with NotifyNYC, installing the Ready NYC app, or ensuring your phone can receive WEA—you will receive emergency alerts on your phone in New York City.\n', include_extracted_content_only_once=False, metadata=None, include_in_memory=False)], all_model_outputs=[{'go_to_url': {'url': 'https://www.nyc.gov', 'new_tab': False}, 'interacted_element': None}, {'wait': {'seconds': 5}, 'interacted_element': None}, {'click_element_by_index': {'index': 7}, 'interacted_element': DOMInteractedElement(node_id=1149, backend_node_id=629, frame_id=None, node_type=<NodeType.ELEMENT_NODE: 1>, node_value='', node_name='BUTTON', attributes={'id': 'global-search-button', 'class': 'cmp-button', 'data-ck': 'xx57dc5d21-53d5-4b01-a6f4-a080902abc4c', 'data-oid': 'cityofnewyorkproduction1oub1837a', 'aria-controls': 'global-search-modal', 'data-open-modal': ''}, bounds=DOMRect(x=1394.15625, y=52.1875, width=128.015625, height=44.0), x_path='html/body/div[2]/div/header/div/div/div/div[2]/div/div/div[3]/button', element_hash=4407204861276460702)}, {'input_text': {'index': 3, 'text': 'emergency alerts phone', 'clear_existing': True}, 'interacted_element': DOMInteractedElement(node_id=2571, backend_node_id=3784, frame_id=None, node_type=<NodeType.ELEMENT_NODE: 1>, node_value='', node_name='TEXTAREA', attributes={'part': 'textarea', 'aria-label': 'Search field with suggestions. Suggestions may be available under this field. To send, press Enter.', 'placeholder': 'Search nyc.gov', 'class': 'placeholder-neutral-dark', 'rows': '1', 'autocomplete': 'off', 'autocapitalize': 'off